  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Whistler Early Booking Ski Offers</h2>
<p>Discover unbeatable early booking offers for thrilling ski holidays in <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a> and enjoy savings of up to 40% for the 2024/25 ski season. *T&amp;Cs apply.</p>
<h3>Experience Whistler: North America's most famous ski resort</h3>
<p>Over 200 trails spread between two peaks (Whistler and Blackcomb Mountains) and linked by the famous Peak2Peak gondola, the resort has become the pride and joy of Canada’s Pacific North West. The resort boasts a mix of chalet-style apartments, inns, lodges, condos, and pedestrian-friendly streets.</p>
<p><a href="#dining" data-anchor="#dining"><img src="/media/13106174/whistler-250-dining-voucher-banner.png" alt="Dining Voucher" data-udi="umb://media/c1348fb3c50d43e181187fafe06055a9" /></a></p>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3}" title="Fairmont Chateau Whistler">Fairmont Chateau Whistler</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 30% | Ends 30.06.24</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dff430bb4aa43bc987c0ce4f4d5b3f3}" title="Fairmont Chateau Whistler"><img src="/media/13084610/fairmont-chateau-whistler-ski-in-ski-out-2.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7070d539cae946afa9b34cb2173728fa" /></a></p>
<p>The Fairmont Chateau Whistler is one of the most prestigious hotels in Whistler, offering exceptionally high standards as the world-renowned hospitality leaders.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/482b29901f9c44c387a35de164fc1b5c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/482b29901f9c44c387a35de164fc1b5c}" title="Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa">Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 40% | Ends 30.06.24</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/482b29901f9c44c387a35de164fc1b5c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/482b29901f9c44c387a35de164fc1b5c}" title="Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa"><img src="/media/13088473/hotel-hilton-whistler.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/b0010b03c4694a89a0e9c5b0a5c937f6" /></a></p>
<p><span>A convenient luxury hotel offering superb value for money, the Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa is a popular hotel for its great location and easy self-catering options.</span><span></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/1f359444cbcd4c98abc81084d2180b62" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1f359444cbcd4c98abc81084d2180b62}" title="Blackcomb Springs Suites">Blackcomb Spring Suites</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 40% | Ends 30.06.24</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/1f359444cbcd4c98abc81084d2180b62" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1f359444cbcd4c98abc81084d2180b62}" title="Blackcomb Springs Suites"><img src="/media/13082067/blackcomb-springs-suites-whistler-front-entrance-winter.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/c019eb54039c4f4c996fc1d6f7d6272d" /></a></p>
<p><span>The Blackcomb Springs Suites enjoys a quiet and wooded slopeside location with ski-in, ski-out access of Blackcomb Mountain.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="#100offer" data-anchor="#100offer"><img src="/media/13106173/whistler-save-100-banner.jpg" alt="Whistler Savings Banner" data-udi="umb://media/6d28a5b720f84e1589fa6bf484782bf3" /></a></p>
<p> </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449}" title="Delta Whistler Village Suites">Delta Whistler Village Suites</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 35% | Ends 31.08.24</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604c5a5d57ac41d991881292b931e449}" title="Delta Whistler Village Suites"><img src="/media/13075014/dwvs-new-exterior.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ec6ccfbdbca04a6eb5c2974c0b6bbb52" /></a></p>
<p><span>Newly renovated, the Delta Whistler Village Suites offers high quality rooms and suites combined with the services and facilities of a full service hotel.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/ec354f3691084941b12a0db826e783d0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ec354f3691084941b12a0db826e783d0}" title="Hotel Aava">Hotel Aava</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 35% | Ends 31.08.24</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802}" title="Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites"><img src="/media/13105784/canada_whistler_hotel_aava_exterior-1-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2a3fee3ae86743cdb4bd69624af16d6a" /></a></p>
<p><span>Hotel Aava is right in the centre of Whistler and has easy access to ski lifts and snow activities, offering value for money and a great base for your adventures.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/acd6842d43524eb99d16dd184771623e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acd6842d43524eb99d16dd184771623e}" title="Hotel Pinnacle Whistler Village">Hotel Pinnacle Whistler Village</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 10% | Ends 31.08.24</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/acd6842d43524eb99d16dd184771623e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acd6842d43524eb99d16dd184771623e}" title="Hotel Pinnacle Whistler Village"><img src="/media/13076321/outdoor-winter-pic.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/9a409b34b73d4be983f6378a7cf9d3d1" /></a></p>
<p><span>Hotel Pinnacle Whistler Village has the best of both worlds with a central location set back from Whistler's main street.</span><span></span></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802}" title="Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites">Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites</a></h4>
<h4 style="color: #e02533;"><strong>Save up to 40% | Ends 31.08.24</strong></h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b38e97f4ff04d62b7d3353afeee5802}" title="Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites"><img src="/media/13087030/crystal-lodge-winter-stroll-web-res.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/be2a320cc70a4956abf3f933a1d6c873" /></a></p>
<p>The modern Crystal Lodge is situated close to restaurants, shops and a two minute walk to the ski lifts for Whistler &amp; Blackcomb Mountain.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b8964cd652f24274a3e3b8c884aaf48e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8964cd652f24274a3e3b8c884aaf48e}" title="Whistler" class="c-btn">View all Whistler Deals</a></p>
<p> </p>
<p><img src="/media/13104122/air-canada-free-ski-carriage.jpg" alt="Air Canada Free Ski Carriage" data-udi="umb://media/0eceedb1e55e40b8bc8f0c47a927dc78" /></p>
<p>Book your flights to Canada with Air Canada to get a free carriage. Includes ski bag &amp; boot bag!</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Whistler Terms &amp; Conditions</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><em>Fairmont Chateau Whistler</em>: Early Bird Offer valid Dec 01 – Dec 24, 2024, Jan 02 – Apr 30, 2025. Offer not available Jan 02, 03, 04, 22, 23, 26, 27, 2025. Applicable for the following room categories: Fairmont, Deluxe View, Deluxe Slopeside, Fairmont Gold rooms (Does not include Suites). Available on new bookings only, no group bookings.   </li>
<li>Early Bird Suite Offer applicable dates: Dec 01 – Dec 19, 2024, Jan 02 – Apr 30, 2025. Not available Jan 02, 03, 04, 22, 23, 26, 27, 2025. Applicable for all Suites and Fairmont Gold Suites. Available on new bookings only, no group bookings.     </li>
<li>Early Bird Single &amp; Double Upgrade Offer applicable dates: Dec 01 – Dec 19, 2024, Jan 02 – Apr 30, 2025. Not available Jan 22, 23, 26, 27, 2025. Applicable for Fairmont Rooms. Available on new bookings only, no group bookings.                  </li>
<li>Long Stay Offer applicable dates: Dec 01 – Dec 24, 2024, Jan 02 – Apr 30, 2025. Not available Jan 02, 03, 04, 22, 23, 26, 27, 2025 Applicable for Fairmont, Deluxe View, Deluxe Slopeside, Fairmont Gold Rooms (Does not include Suites). Available on new bookings only, no group bookings.                                      </li>
<li><em>Crystal Lodge</em>: EBO not valid between Dec 25 2024 - Jan 1 2025 and Feb 14 - 22 2025. Available on new bookings only, no group bookings.                   </li>
<li id="dining"><em>Dining Voucher</em>: New bookings of 10+ nights to Whistler, for winter 24/25, will receive $250 CAD in-resort credits. The minimum nights must be in Whistler and cannot include pre/post stays in other destinations. Offer valid until August 31st but can be withdrawn at any time/ until stocks last.<br />- A family travelling together would be 1 booking<br />- A couple travelling would be 1 booking<br />- Two separate families who book together, would get 2 vouchers categories except Suites.</li>
<li><em>Hilton Whistler Resort &amp; Spa</em>: Valid on Studio, Hilton Room, Premier Studio, Signature Spa, Jr Family Combo, and Hilton Family Combo. Applicable for bookings accommodated from 15-20 December 2024, 21 December 2024 - 3 January 2025, 4 January - 13 February 2025, 23 February - 20 April 2025.</li>
<li><em>Delta Whistler Village Suites</em>: Valid in one and two bedroom suites only. Valid for travel 21 Nov - 24 Dec 25 and 23 Mar - 30 Apr 25. Not valid 25 Dec 24 - 1 Jan 25. 2 Jan - 22 Mar 25</li>
<li><em>Hotel Aava</em>: For stays between 21 November 2024 and 30 April 2025</li>
<li id="100offer"><em>Hotel Pinnacle Whistler Village</em>: Minimum stay 2 nights available Sunday to Thursdays </li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Save £100pp on Whistler ski holidays T&amp;Cs</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Only applicable when adding a 5 day + lift pass to your holiday at the time of booking and booked with Air Canada flights</li>
<li>Valid on new bookings only</li>
<li>Offer cannot be booked online, please call our reservations team to book</li>
<li>Offer ends 15th November 2024</li>
<li>Only applicable when adding a 5 day + lift pass to your holiday at the time of booking</li>
<li>Offer is available for bookings made between Friday 7<sup>th</sup> June – Friday 15th November</li>
<li>Offer is subject to availability and may be removed at any time</li>
<li>Offer can be combined with other Whistler savings on accommodation</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
